profile: "West Quebec Shed Company" We are manufactures custom Cottages, Coach Homes Small Bunkhouses and Quality built sheds in all sizes. All of our products come fully assembled and delivered right to you location. We also offer all of our models in kit form that is Pre-Assembled and Re-Assembled on site. Our shed yard locations are Highway 105 in Alcove PQ (Wakefield) and Highway 307 St. Pierre PQ. Choose from board and batten, kiln dried Dutch Lap siding, Duratemp 50 year warranty siding. We have many models that you can choose from. Engineered certified meeting all provincial building standards for Ontario and Quebec.
